(1270, 365, 'SEAS Teaching Practicum', 'Y', 2011, 8195, 'Y', 'Reading and Research', 'Graduate Course', 'Computer Science', 0, '', '', 'Gain effective skills for teaching applied sciences. Topics: presentation and communication, lesson planning, classroom practice, office hours and 1-on-1 interactions, feedback, assessment, and working with course staff. Seminar style with an emphasis on observation, practice, feedback, discussion, and reflection.', '', ''),
