(2748, 3350, 'Laboratory Methods in Primate and Human Nutrition', 'Y', 2011, 62293, 'Y', 'Laboratory Research', 'Primarily for Graduates', 'Human Evolutionary Biology', 0, '', '', 'Independent laboratory study in the biochemical analysis of plant and animal foods, and of human and animal digestive physiology and feeding behavior.', '', ''),
